    "research": "Gmail compose window has autocomplete dropdown that blocks subsequent field clicks. Pressing Enter accepts autocomplete and closes dropdown. Ctrl+Enter keyboard shortcut is more reliable than clicking Send button. Explicit field clicks are more reliable than Tab navigation due to dynamic UI.",
    "strategy": "Load saved session for instant access. Click compose button, wait for window. Fill To field with human typing, press Enter to accept autocomplete. Click Subject field explicitly, fill with typing. Click Body field explicitly, fill with typing. Send with Ctrl+Enter keyboard shortcut.",
